      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, what do you mean by \"rogue processes\" acting like goblins? i'm not sure how that translates to the actual code. can you just explain the technical fix for the session lock and that null pointer without the metaphors? i need to report a concrete cause to my lead.",
      "source": "evaluator"
